Class VariableEliminator.WeightedMinFill

    Enclosing class:
    VariableEliminator

    public static class VariableEliminator.WeightedMinFill
extends VariableEliminator.CostFunction
    Similar to VariableEliminator.MinFill but instead of counting edges that would be added, it counts the sum of the weights of added edges where the weight is the product of the domain cardinalities at each end.

    Get instance from VariableEliminator.VariableCost.WEIGHTED_MIN_FILL.
